== fn execute/1 origin=execute ==
  sig: (empty_fork_collection.EmptyForkCollectionInput) -> Result(empty_fork_collection.EmptyForkCollectionOutcome, AwlError)
  T-EXEC fields=[docs:List(empty_fork_collection.Doc)] entry=step_check_all args=[0]
